summary: An ordinance providing for the repair and resurfacing of the roadway portion of West Roxbury Street from 4th Avenue Southwest to 16th Avenue Southwest, lying within the corporate limits of the City of Seattle; authorizing the improvement in the same manner of the roadway portion of West Roxbury Street, lying in King County, from 4th Avenue Southwest to 16th Avenue Southwest, upon payment of the cost of such work by King County; and appropriating money from the City Street Fund for the City's portion of said work.
